metadata.name: Angels of rain
metadata.description:
Suppressed, raped, torn apart and killed. This is the story of a nation being slaughtered for their basic rights after close to half a century of dictatorship. This is more than feminism, more than any of us. This is about humanity. In memory of Mahsa. In memory of Nika. For all the Iranians. The least I could dedicate to my people especially the brave women of Iran.

Resolution : 1842 x2304 (4K UHD)
